				<h3 id="post-3309"><a href="http://samablog.robsama.com/?p=3309" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Limbaugh &#8211; Shark &#8211; Jump">Limbaugh &#8211; Shark &#8211; Jump</a></h3>
				<small>Wednesday, March 19th, 2008</small>

				<div class="entry">
					<p><a href="http://marcambinder.theatlantic.com/archives/2008/03/rush_limbaugh_reacts.php">Rush Limbaugh jumped the shark</a> today.</p>
				</div>

				<p class="postmetadata">Tags: <a href="http://samablog.robsama.com/?tag=jump-the-shark" rel="tag">Jump The Shark</a>, <a href="http://samablog.robsama.com/?tag=rush-limbaugh" rel="tag">Rush Limbaugh</a><br /> Posted in <a href="http://samablog.robsama.com/?cat=4" title="View all posts in News &amp; Politics" rel="category">News & Politics</a> |   <a href="http://samablog.robsama.com/?p=3309#comments" title="Comment on Limbaugh &#8211; Shark &#8211; Jump">2 Comments &#187;</a></p>

