				<small>Friday, March 14th, 2008</small>

				<div class="entry">
					<p>I&#8217;ve been obsessing over the song, Slip Inside This House by the 13th Floor Elevators for a while now.  Check out the <a href="http://www.lyrics007.com/13th%20Floor%20Elevators%20Lyrics/Slip%20Inside%20This%20House%20Lyrics.html">lyrics</a>.</p>
